      {'h': '6. Enter the estimated number of athletes',
       'b': 'For each selected category, a <b>No. of athletes</b> field appears. Fill in your estimate and click <b>Continue</b>.',
       'img': 'img/en/06-num-atletas.png', 'cap': 'With categories selected, enter the athlete count and click Continue.'},
      {'h': '7. Step 3 · Create your password',
       'b': 'Set a password of <b>at least 8 characters</b> and repeat it in the confirmation field.',
       'img': 'img/en/07-senha.png', 'cap': 'Password and confirmation fields in Step 3.'},
      {'h': '8. Accept the terms and click “Create Account”',
       'b': 'Read the Terms and Conditions, check <b>“I have read and accept the terms and conditions”</b> (left arrow) and click <b>Create Account</b> (right arrow).',
       'img': 'img/en/08-termos-criar-conta.png', 'cap': 'Check the terms box and finish with Create Account.'},
