      {'h': '5. Information tab · Fees, deadlines and spots',
       'b': 'Everything your team needs to know before paying: confirmation windows (Jul 7–12 priority for pre-registered; Jul 13–20 open to any team), the two pricing options, installments, required equipment and lodging/logistics. <b>Attention: spots per category are limited</b> and filled by order of first-installment payment — once a category is full, registration closes.'},
